What you need to know:  Odera said the return of Kubu gives him different options at his backline.“I now have to pick between Kubu and Dominic Coulson with Geoffrey Ominde also offering something different.“Vincent Onyala and John Okoth seem to be settling at centre with Collins Injera at the wing. The power of Bilda Ogeta, Derrick Ashiundu and Jacob Ojee coming in with experience makes the backline quite exciting,” said Odera.